{"tid":1089044,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"［英國撚］Egg benedict比all day breakfast更值得欣賞","createTime":"2019-04-02T13:08:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-08T09:47:20.000Z","uid":221748,"like":52,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"ec10d0b25420f47e1434cd831ce445d8eed1436c","tid":1089044,"uid":221748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T13:08:22.000Z","msg":"好多人一諗起英國既早餐就係all day breakfast <br />\n其實根本就係垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又易煮 又唔好食<br />\n基本上 一個鍋已經可以煮晒成個all day breakfast <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BehsLFX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBehsLFX.png&h=7d7bbd03&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nEgg Benedict 雖然比港女搞臭個朵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但其實不知好幾多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 淨係個荷蘭醬<br />\n每間店都有自己配方 而且一煮得唔好 就會break 就要重煮<br />\n技術上已經大勝all day breakfast <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 每次一定叫多醬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n流心蛋 又要睇住個時間 <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JdUVUBp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJdUVUBp.png&h=423dec02&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n仲有好多變化 例如用三文魚就叫 egg Royale <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NW5FmgZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNW5FmgZ.png&h=bc723185&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n個味食落 又creamy<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />又夠營養<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n屌打 all day breakfast 啦<br />\n<br />\n我為咗搵英國既好食物 真金白銀周圍食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之後介紹比大家 大家中意可以follow<br />\nIg: <a href=\"https://instagram.com/foodkiller_dk?utm_source=ig_profile_share&amp;igshid=1r6fntnocpz34\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Ffoodkiller_dk%3Futm_source%3Dig_profile_share%26igshid%3D1r6fntnocpz34&d=hsG%2BTWPyVhMSOc%2FhwZgu%2BgKWJX65Gw4YGtkQ1cmlXhw%3D&h=04980df5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/foodkiller_dk?utm_source=ig_profile_share&amp;igshid=1r6fntnocpz34</a>"},{"pid":"345b36f13bbce81e51e3e58e2d63a7039afc3862","tid":1089044,"uid":166890,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T14:17:52.000Z","msg":"一定係 除非唔係"},{"pid":"3b2a86f51527a7ec0d7ab51a31b43776e28197e1","tid":1089044,"uid":221748,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"345b36f13bbce81e51e3e58e2d63a7039afc3862","tid":1089044,"uid":166890,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T14:17:52.000Z","msg":"一定係 除非唔係"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T14:37:46.000Z","msg":"淨係果兩張egg Benedict 個汁已經唔同色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家既recipe 唔同"},{"pid":"a5bf908cb81b7b8623cea54861fd5ddc1fca6ed6","tid":1089044,"uid":208241,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T15:20:58.000Z","msg":"Hollandaise sauce其實好易整，屋企5分鐘都整到，隻蛋水滾落8分鐘到上來就係流心，功夫仲少過all day breakfast<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54e36151656a9d5f3b498c0a3c394e3a0d8c3a49","tid":1089044,"uid":221748,"like":1,"dislike":8,"score":-7,"quote":{"pid":"a5bf908cb81b7b8623cea54861fd5ddc1fca6ed6","tid":1089044,"uid":208241,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T15:20:58.000Z","msg":"Hollandaise sauce其實好易整，屋企5分鐘都整到，隻蛋水滾落8分鐘到上來就係流心，功夫仲少過all day breakfast<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T15:42:13.000Z","msg":"要慢慢搞架喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n太多牛油又唔得 太少又唔得"},{"pid":"b6648ac103e33f9e355d327ed511db457b9d0623","tid":1089044,"uid":208241,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":